==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-eɪʒən|-eɪʒən]]

===Noun===
'''equation''' (''plural'' '''equations''')

# {{math}} An assertion that two [[expression]]s are equal, expressed by writing the two expressions separated by an [[equal sign]].

